org.sql: SELECT versions.* FROM versions INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = versions.project_id WHERE projects.lft >= 6 AND projects.rgt <= 7 AND projects.status <> 9 AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'issue_tracking') IS NOT NULL AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13))
